(firstQuint)Vitamin D Substitution During Winter Time.

 Vitamin D substitution is widely recommended.

 Suggested substitution doses are increasing over the time.

 No exact body requirement is known for patients with IBD at present.

 Aim of the study was to confirm substitution dose obtained from model.

